HEADWORD: Cartage
<hw>Cart"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of carrying in a cart.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The price paid for carting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

